name: Oktoberfest
summary: Step into Oktoberfest, the social VR fun fair packed with fun for everyone!  🎢 Hop on wild rides and enjoy a typical theme park atmosphere 🎮 Compete with others in multiplayer games based on real attractions 🍺 Try the new Barrel Hunt game for tag-like fun 💀 Team up for spooky co-op combat in Haunting Grounds 🐾 Adopt cute pets 🧍‍♂️ Customize your avatar and show off your style  Grab your friends - there’s always something happening at Oktoberfest!  👉 Join the community: bit.ly/OktoberfestVRDiscord
